flowchart TD
    Start((Start Assessment)) --> Intro[Show Instructions & Privacy Notice]
    
    Intro --> DisplayQ[Display Question]
    DisplayQ --> Answer[User Provides Answer]
    
    Answer --> CriticalCheck{Is Answer \n Weight = 50?}
    
    CriticalCheck -- Yes --> Emergency[Stop Assessment Immediately]
    Emergency --> AlertAdmin[SQL: Insert High-Risk Log]
    AlertAdmin --> ShowHotlines[Display Emergency Support & Crisis Contacts]
    ShowHotlines --> End((End - Emergency Path))

    CriticalCheck -- No --> LastQ{Is it the \n Last Question?}
    LastQ -- No --> DisplayQ
    
    LastQ -- Yes --> Calc[AI Engine: Calculate Category Scores]
    Calc --> SaveResults[SQL: Save Assessment Result]
    
    SaveResults --> ScoreAnalysis{Top Score \n Category?}
    
    ScoreAnalysis -- "Score > 15" --> Specialized[Recommend Specialized Specialist \n e.g., CBT, Child Psych]
    ScoreAnalysis -- "Score 10-15" --> Mixed[Recommend General Counselor / \n Support Group]
    ScoreAnalysis -- "Score < 10" --> General[Recommend Wellness Content / \n General Lounge]

    Specialized --> Action[User Action: Book or Join]
    Mixed --> Action
    General --> Action
    
    Action --> Dashboard[Return to Dashboard]
    Dashboard --> End2((End - Normal Path))